{
  "stem": "19807.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in-- that's 1941, when the edict came out, and we're sitting in temple, and the Nazis are advancing, and my father-- when the rabbi sang, and you have chosen them from all the people, my father very quietly said, well, choose somebody else already.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But, be as it may, he had very strong-- strong beliefs that everything will turn out OK.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those are the days when he-- he really began to-- to get active with me, to make sure that I would be able to leave the country.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is when I got involved with the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And through the [INAUDIBLE], it took me two years to get my papers in order.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then through the [INAUDIBLE], we came to-- to Palestine at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let-- Let's talk a little bit more about your prewar experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Tell me about your religious background.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What was that like for you, growing up?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our religious background was actually, we are Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in a sense, we're conservative.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The reason I'm saying we were Orthodox, because in temple, the women would sit separately from the men.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as far as the rest of the-- the-- the way, it was very, very progressive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole country was very progressive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Jews were very progressive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But our faith, if I remember very, very well, I remember, is I was only five years old, 5 and 1/2 years old, when my mother and my father enrolled me into Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we went to-- into kindergarten there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, I just brought you a picture to see that we had a play about Purim.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
